    Analysis: Interval of confidence

    interval.confidence.Rd

    Interval of confidence in model regression

    interval.confidence(model)

    Arguments

    model

    Object analysis

    Value

    Return in the interval of confidence

    Author

    Gabriel Danilo Shimizu
